(3595, 1, '2022-10-19 03:23:24', '2022-10-18 20:23:24', '<p>Indonesia has a wealth of extraordinary spices in the world that made other nations come long before the empire era. Spices are a group of plants that have a very strong taste and aroma and also a good plant for treatment.</p><p>We have highly trained inspectors to ensure your item reaches our strict standards, we ensure that you receive only the best quality items.</p>		\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"621\" src=\"https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-1024x621.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-1024x621.jpg 1024w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-300x182.jpg 300w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices.jpg 1360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n		Indonesia is abundant with fertile soils and is a major producer of a wide variety of tropical agricultural products for the global market.\nThe global market demand for organic spices, essential oils and extracts used for food, cosmetics and medicinal products is high. The production of such natural goods can provide income for the people and protect biodiversity.		\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"621\" src=\"https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-1024x621.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-1024x621.jpg 1024w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-300x182.jpg 300w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cyindo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/herbs-spices.jpg 1360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3565-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-19 03:23:24', '2022-10-18 20:23:24', '', 3565, 'https://cyindo.com/3565-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
